{"tid":1132160,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［劇透］mcu係咪應該要避免平行世界設定？","createTime":"2019-04-30T06:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T10:54:28.000Z","uid":84511,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"51a906456d335713234282c0536df1aa5397a886","tid":1132160,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"本身endgame有好多時間旅行嘅bug都可以用無限寶石或其他手段拆<br />\n而唔洗借平行世界設定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身我都覺得mcu會兜<br />\n但羅素兄弟竟然親口承認有平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平行世界呢個設定係有好大代價<br />\n會令代入感下降 劇情上不受控<br />\n無法解釋點解其他平行時空嘅惡人唔出現係呢邊<br />\nthanos個計劃亦變到好低級<br />\n要去哂時空啪手指先算任務完成<br />\n同埋以後所有自我犧牲嘅場景亦都顯得戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲bug點拆大家應該討論過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都再提一提點去解決單一時空觀下解決（類）祖父悖論<br />\n<br />\nloki拎石走咗只需要美隊係loki拎石走咗之後一秒去佢轉走嘅地方打鳩暈佢送返佢返2012同一個位 呢啲做法好簡單就諗到<br />\n2014thonas大軍成堆人過哂嚟 變哂灰 所以有祖父悖論<br />\n可以話係tony啪手指嗰下係一路將佢地變灰<br />\n一路係2014年還原返佢地出嚟並且消除記憶 tony話哂係天才 未必無諗到呢樣嘢<br />\n總之有六石就任得你講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講就係<br />\nmcu其實係有方法保留單一時空呢個預設 無必要加設定有平行時空<br />\n<br />\n如果得一個時空代表你回到過去做嘅嘢係有限制 因為必須要避免太大嘅動作<br />\n例如講time travel嘅哲學討論會認為係同一個時空下<br />\n你係會因某啲原因無辦法殺到你嘅祖父 因為每一個時間點嘅事其實定咗<br />\n你可能會開唔到槍啦 或者點啦<br />\n<br />\n但有平行世界就代表你點玩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家2012定咗得垃圾avengers<br />\n叫齊新avengers返2012實夠打掛<br />\n如果佢阻你直頭殺哂成佢地都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩大事咪又去各個時空借石<br />\n抽生死籤搵條友用六石還原一切<br />\n隔離平行時空會變成點根本唔關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaf54f2b9561357a408a1462584dfe1cdafede8","tid":1132160,"uid":34123,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"MCU自己本身已經係一個平行世界, Earth-199999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7cabf713c09e1b6a2b9b1d04a9b3ef1269430c","tid":1132160,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"咁Marvel漫畫本身就係玩多宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f3ecb8de433211c618902b6adaf7d76455d80e","tid":1132160,"uid":104171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"如果佢真係咁玩<br />\n咁唔洗睇mcu啦睇翻漫畫咪得<br />\nn咁多個平行世界真係叫大眾點維持興趣<br />\n成日話漫畫點點點<br />\nmcu係cinematic唔係comic"},{"pid":"ab3f48b361ec2ffac2ca9a2620d7336c5112cdf8","tid":1132160,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"DC電視劇咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27dc9a9e4cf32f99f19bb623a6b29cea5225998","tid":1132160,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"冷靜..佢呢套玩呢樣野 未必之後都會咁玩 TONY死左 未必寫到有個人可以整番部野出黎穿黎穿去 同埋個gps穩定器都冇埋既話 可能唔會再寫太多量子領域既野"},{"pid":"4a9cc1c379509d464c8a365b590957656a2c3cdb","tid":1132160,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27dc9a9e4cf32f99f19bb623a6b29cea5225998","tid":1132160,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"冷靜..佢呢套玩呢樣野 未必之後都會咁玩 TONY死左 未必寫到有個人可以整番部野出黎穿黎穿去 同埋個gps穩定器都冇埋既話 可能唔會再寫太多量子領域既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"CA番去還石果部呢???"},{"pid":"a36314923263d574da045f7cf0144b150c4022be","tid":1132160,"uid":92680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:28:28.000Z","msg":"agent of shield仲早過endgame玩"},{"pid":"5a347bdf9d4d94a6611e027bdafcdb99944544fa","tid":1132160,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a9cc1c379509d464c8a365b590957656a2c3cdb","tid":1132160,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27dc9a9e4cf32f99f19bb623a6b29cea5225998","tid":1132160,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"冷靜..佢呢套玩呢樣野 未必之後都會咁玩 TONY死左 未必寫到有個人可以整番部野出黎穿黎穿去 同埋個gps穩定器都冇埋既話 可能唔會再寫太多量子領域既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"CA番去還石果部呢???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"冇手上面個舊野就咁用部機穿越有機會變bb 所以個部野可能未必會再用 <br />\n我自己都唔希望mcu再玩太多關於時間線既野 真係好易有bug 而且其實唔玩時間都仲有好多野可以玩 希望只係玩呢一集 之後都唔好再玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffe2b047e3ccd84a5e4729a22fb31476d103fe8","tid":1132160,"uid":119545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"樓主有無睇Ant Man....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eb8a05ae4a34d7259c8d2d17d25385b63da237","tid":1132160,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"點解要咁著重所有時間線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06af90758db0fba750456d90d700240440325dab","tid":1132160,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ca鬼知洛基轉左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15786466be399f8aa971eab1f035d172f7e3da06","tid":1132160,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"唯有希望佢係想將xmen個面既time travel 交錯寫埋一齊 漫畫係咪有個管時間既大佬 btw佢d編劇係咪唔睇dc㗎 至少flash要補補..."},{"pid":"fc7861eb44e4a03ae3f0939556ec5945ca997f3e","tid":1132160,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06af90758db0fba750456d90d700240440325dab","tid":1132160,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ca鬼知洛基轉左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"係㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n操作上係一個難題<br />\n但至少有解決呢個bug嘅可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f4585ec3f9472833f768df4dde75940f0264a7","tid":1132160,"uid":89496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"漫畫內戰係一個時空<br />\nMCU又係另一個時空<br />\n可以有MCU時間1,MCU時間2,MCU時間3, 如此類推<br />\n要解一定解到"},{"pid":"bdd485952b33d967bcd9476b0b9f3b169e160e43","tid":1132160,"uid":23629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06af90758db0fba750456d90d700240440325dab","tid":1132160,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ca鬼知洛基轉左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"其實佢地都好似唔係太care其他時間線<br />\n正如古一都只係唔想Hulk喺佢條時間線拎走time stone<br />\nCA同IM又唔care洛基去咗邊，一心諗去第二度拎粒space stone"},{"pid":"cc496e92d59bff8f970b11c73282e0e6d4b4b0c2","tid":1132160,"uid":41453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"Marvel做野駛你教？<br />\n留條尾等三十年後復仇者第16集用CG做番第一代美隊Iron Man出黎同新一代並肩作戰<br />\n全世界含淚十刷探老朋友<br />\n全球二百億美金票房不是夢啦"},{"pid":"ea6c24efa37749677b0378514c39597111b9dcd1","tid":1132160,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"漫畫本身都成日用平行宇宙將d人氣角色彈出彈入，例如狼人死咗，之後佢又將平行宇宙個老狼人引入去主宇宙"},{"pid":"9c3ba515d0f00140568aaab8ac58dd271f37fe70","tid":1132160,"uid":119716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd485952b33d967bcd9476b0b9f3b169e160e43","tid":1132160,"uid":23629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06af90758db0fba750456d90d700240440325dab","tid":1132160,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ca鬼知洛基轉左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"其實佢地都好似唔係太care其他時間線<br />\n正如古一都只係唔想Hulk喺佢條時間線拎走time stone<br />\nCA同IM又唔care洛基去咗邊，一心諗去第二度拎粒space stone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"Loki個到應該都係要等影集個到解畫架啦<br />\n